    "Elastic Security does not provide built-in vulnerability scanning capability.",
    "In terms of cyber threat intelligence, two of the evaluated SIEMs were found to have built-in threat intelligence capability.",
    "Elastic Security has a threat intelligence module that ingests threat data from various sources.",
    "This data is then utilized to detect malicious events via indicator match rules.",
    "This threat data is also used to add additional context to enrich the incoming traffic."
